Package com.rabbitmq.tools.jsonrpc

Class DefaultJsonRpcMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rabbitmq.tools.jsonrpc.DefaultJsonRpcMapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JsonRpcMapper
    public class DefaultJsonRpcMapper
extends Object
implements JsonRpcMapper
    Deprecated.
    use JacksonJsonRpcMapper instead
    Simple JsonRpcMapper based on homegrown JSON utilities. Handles integers, doubles, strings, booleans, and arrays of those types.

    For a more comprehensive set of features, use JacksonJsonRpcMapper.

    Will be removed in 6.0

    Since:
    4.8.0
    See Also:
    JsonRpcMapper, JacksonJsonRpcMapper
